{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sum-to-100","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Jumlisha hadi 100","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tafuta suluhisho za changamoto ya <em>jumlisha hadi mia moja</em>.</p>\n<p>Umetni matematičke operatore <strong>+</strong> ili <strong>−</strong> (sabiranje ili oduzimanje) ispred bilo koje cifre u nizu <strong>123456789</strong> tako da dobijeni izraz daje određeni zbir (u ovom poznatom primeru <strong>100</strong>).</p>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<pre><b>123 + 4 - 5 + 67 - 89 = 100</b></pre>\n</section>","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8043","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napiši funkciju koja prihvata broj kao argument. Funkcija treba da vrati niz koji sadrži sva rešenja za taj broj. Rešenja treba da budu niske koje predstavljaju matematičke izraze, na primer: <code>\"1+23-456+78-9\"</code>. Sortiraj niz pre nego što ga vratiš.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302335,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sum-to-100"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sumTo100(n) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100</code> treba da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof sumTo100 == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100(199)</code> treba da vrati niz.</p>","testString":"assert(Array.isArray(sumTo100(199)));"},{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100(199)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>[\"-1+2-3+45+67+89\", \"123-4+5+6+78-9\", \"123-4+56+7+8+9\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(sumTo100(199), [\n  '-1+2-3+45+67+89',\n  '123-4+5+6+78-9',\n  '123-4+56+7+8+9'\n]);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100(209)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[\"1+234+56+7-89\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(sumTo100(209), ['1+234+56+7-89']);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100(243)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[\"-1-234+567-89\", \"-12+345+6-7-89\", \"123+45+6+78-9\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(sumTo100(243), [\n  '-1-234+567-89',\n  '-12+345+6-7-89',\n  '123+45+6+78-9'\n]);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumTo100(197)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[\"1-2-3+45+67+89\", \"12+34-5+67+89\", \"123+4-5+6+78-9\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(sumTo100(197), [\n  '1-2-3+45+67+89',\n  '12+34-5+67+89',\n  '123+4-5+6+78-9'\n]);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"sum-to-100","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sutherland-hodgman-polygon-clipping","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sum-of-squares","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8043","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sum-to-100"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}